#. type: Plain text
#: source/server_admin/topics/login-settings/remember-me.adoc:7
msgid ""
"If a logged in user closes their browser, their session is destroyed and "
"they will have to log in again.  You can set things up so that if a user "
"checks a _remember me_ checkbox, they will remain logged in even if the "
"browser is closed.  This basically turns the login cookie from a session-"
"only cookie to a persistence cookie."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: source/server_admin/topics/login-settings/remember-me.adoc:9
msgid ""
"To enable this feature go to `Realm Settings` left menu item and click on "
"the `Login` tab and turn on the `Remember Me` switch:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: source/server_admin/topics/login-settings/remember-me.adoc:14
msgid ""
"Once you save this setting, a `remember me` checkbox will be displayed on "
"the realm's login page."
msgstr ""

